snippet.title: Year 7 Season 1: Demon Veil Reveal Panel | Tom Clancy’s Rainbow Six Siege
snippet.description: Rainbow Six Siege will be kicking off Year 7 with an ambitious first season, Demon Veil! Watch to learn about the new map, Team Deathmatch and new Operator.
